<p align="center"><h1><font color="red">TOOLS</font></h1></p> 


<br />
<p align="left"><h2>Sample tools</h2></p> 

<p align="justify">When a sample is selected, the "tools" menu offers several features:
<ul>
	<li><b>Trim to end loop</b><br />
	If a loop is defined for the selected sample, the software will cut the sound after the end of the loop (leaving a margin of 8 samples).
	</li>
